This paper is about using evolutionary algorithms to optimize neural network structures, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper discusses the performance of these networks, which could also fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions using these networks for image recognition tasks, which could fall under computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper discusses using these networks for control tasks, which could fall under systems and control (cs.SY).
